Package pkgMain

Class Plant

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Plant
public class Plant
extends java.lang.Object
Creates a Plant object to be used in the Garden Designer Program

This class creates Plant objects based on read-in values from the plantData.csv file.

Author:
mweis
